%% Diagram: Retry with exponential backoff and DLQ
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Worker
    participant P as Provider (FCM/APNs/SES)
    participant RS as Retry Scheduler
    participant DLQ as Dead Letter Queue
    participant M as Metrics

    W->>P: Send notification (attempt 1)
    P-->>W: 5xx / 429 / transient
    W->>RS: Schedule retry @ t+1s ±jitter
    RS->>W: Re-deliver (attempt 2)
    W->>P: Send (attempt 2)
    P-->>W: 5xx / 429 / transient
    W->>RS: Schedule retry @ t+2s ±jitter
    Note over W,RS: Backoff: 1s, 2s, 4s, 8s, ... cap 5min
    RS->>W: Re-deliver (attempt N)
    W->>P: Send (attempt N)
    P-->>W: 5xx / 429 / transient
    W->>DLQ: Enqueue (max attempts exceeded)
    W->>M: Increment notifications.dlq.count
